        <num>31-7-357</num>
        <content>
          <p>Each application form provided by a facility to an applicant shall conspicuously state the following: "FOR THIS TYPE OF EMPLOYMENT, STATE LAW REQUIRES A NATIONAL AND STATE BACKGROUND CHECK AS A CONDITION OF EMPLOYMENT."</p>
